    <div class="container">
        <div class="row justify-content-center">
            <div class="col-md-12 col-lg-9"><p class="ff3" style="font-size:22px;">TOGL’s layer is differential and capable of learning topological representations, making it more expressive than GNNs. Moreover, TOGL can be easily integrated into any type of GNN to increase expressivity in graph learning tasks by making it “topology-aware.”</p></div></div></div></section><section data-bs-version="5.1" class="image3 cid-tt612oXwA9" id="image3-5" style="padding-top:0px; padding-bottom:0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">
